-
‚û°Ô∏èSchedule - By schedule i mean flexible routine. üòâ We don‚Äôt want a strict schedule. That will drive you crazy. This is why I love wake windows. It eliminates the ‚Äúset times‚Äù but gives you a good range and allows you to go with the flow a little bit more. We want naps and bedtime to be within the same half hour range ideally, but if baby takes longer to fall asleep while you‚Äôre away don‚Äôt stress about it! 
-
‚û°Ô∏èRecreate that home environment! Dark room, noise machine, comfort items like loveys, and don‚Äôt forget that sleep sack! We love our travel blackout curtain! Gro Anywhere Blind from Amazon! 
-
‚û°Ô∏è Maintain the same bedtime and nap routine. This is key. All of your routine steps help cue your baby‚Äôs brain for sleep. 
-
‚û°Ô∏è Time zone! If you are going somewhere with an hour or two time difference, try and keep your little one on the same time zone as where you live. If that‚Äôs not possible or if you are travelling further with a larger time zone, try and meet somewhere in the middle. 
-
‚û°Ô∏èCrib sheet - since babies sleep on only a crib sheet this is what they smell and touch all night. When they are in a pitch black room and can‚Äôt see what‚Äôs around them, the feel and smell of that sheet will be a huge factor in creating that familiar calm feeling 
-
‚û°Ô∏èRelax! Remember it‚Äôs your vacation too! Sleep will not be perfect when you‚Äôre away and that‚Äôs ok! Cut yourself some slack and cut baby some slack. Expect that naps won‚Äôt be as good and that your little one may need some extra reassurance. Do your best not to fall into bad habits or create/re-pick up sleep crutches. When you return home fall back into your healthy sleep habits
-
If you‚Äôre struggling with sleep, you don‚Äôt have to! If you haven‚Äôt yet created healthy sleep habits or are looking for ways to get your baby to sleep longer stretches, break sleep associations, and get that full night‚Äôs rest my eBooks or Individualized Sleep Plan can help you and your family get the rest you deserve. ü§ç";}i:225;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:226;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:2;}i:227;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEvSiRuhai8";}i:228;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:238:"https://scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/118728601_336640707694286_3879517469485069401_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_ohc=RVdT7KIA2csAX-snq1Q&oh=37f145bc50376f5cb20f194d4938a216&oe=5F7BB2D1";}i:229;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:230;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:34709298781;}i:231;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:232;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:233;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:234;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391211073402218097";}i:235;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEvSc1VHqZx";}i:236;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599274594;}i:237;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:326:"Alhamdulillah Amanah, Paket Dijamin Pasti Sampai üòÅ.
